title: Braun Stowman, The Biggest Dude In WWE, Is A Wonderfully On Tinder
text:
Braun Stowman, The Biggest Dude In WWE, Is A Wonderfully On Tinder Nate | 
Braun Strowman is a big dude. 
A really big dude. 
And here he is, just swiping away on Tinder, trying to find a bae like everyone else. Doesn’t matter if you’re a 5 foot blogger or a 400 pound monster, all you wanna do is get your swipes in and find that special someone. Really makes me feel like we’re all in this battle together. All we wanna do is lift weights, eat steaks, and match a loose-moraled girl on a dating app. Poetic, really.
